{"about_the_game":"<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Meet Morps!</h2></strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/977510/extras/1_-_Different_Morp_Showcase.gif?t=1740398802\" /><br><br>Time to Morp is a sandbox colony sim designed for both single and multiplayer. Build a base, gather resources, discover new technology and learn about Morps - curious little creatures that inhabit the planet.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/977510/extras/2_Farming.gif?t=1740398802\" /><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Play your way!</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>1-4 players</strong> - Time to Morp is a great solo experience, but it is even more fun with friends!<br></li><li><strong>Your own cozy city</strong> - Build how you like, decorate, plant trees or terraform everything around you!<br></li><li><strong>Play with Morps</strong> - The world is filled with cute and unique creatures - they will help you build, gather resources, and aid in exploration.<br></li><li><strong>Farm and Cook</strong> - Plant your crops, water, harvest, and cook delicious dishes!</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/977510/extras/2_-_Quests_and_NPCs.gif?t=1740398802\" /><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Make new friends!</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>You are never alone</strong> - Meet the Crew, make friends, assist them with tasks, or explore the world together!<br></li><li><strong>Explore vast worlds</strong> - The world is filled with different biomes, events, activities, unique resources and secrets!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Toys and Abilities</strong> - Unlock Glider, Balloons and Hoverboard, or pretend you are a bush to scare your friends!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/977510/extras/3_-_Multiplayer.gif?t=1740398802\" /><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Use your tech!</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Automate everything</strong> - You can water, gather or move everything yourself. Or use tools to do it for you!<br></li><li><strong>Unlock the technology</strong> - From Pumps for transportation, to Ziplines for faster travel, and so much more!</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/977510/extras/4_-_Automation_.gif?t=1740398802\" /><br><br>As an Intern on your first mission, you have an opportunity to prove yourself, befriend the Crew, or discover secrets of this unknown planet! Follow the story to find the source of a SOS signal that brought you here, help creatures in distress, and help a lost soul to rejoin her family.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/977510/extras/5_-_Playing_with_Morps.gif?t=1740398802\" /></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"One very smart Intern","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/977510/f4b28145e060ba03e524614b90de690f7343b9b0.jpg"},{"name":"Time to Style","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/977510/f78dc5a65abb92c3a4679274fe3d1c4b0cff0a87.jpg"},{"name":"Mission Accomplished","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/977510/72cbd6cea530fe9766ebad940269265b15bb60b2.jpg"},{"name":"Fauna Savior","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/977510/688192018ce52f5a61af6a27c94f7188cb8b05c6.jpg"},{"name":"Solid Ground","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/977510/ab7a53c5e5bf976fbba6c4f4c060061cec731b50.jpg"},{"name":"Morp Master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/977510/3f0558f674cd9bdb05b1b63f5618287ff6574dd9.jpg"},{"name":"Friends Foreve